"  Pastry for a double-crust 9-in. pie (refrigerated or homemade)","5 cups peeled and thinly sliced tart apples, such as Granny Smith","1/2 cup packed light brown sugar","1/8 teaspoon salt","1 teaspoon cinnamon","1/2 teaspoon ground cardamom","3 tablespoons chopped candied ginger","1 tablespoon lemon juice","1 tablespoon cornstarch"